nodes.text: Galek was a human female who served as a lieutenant and flight instructor in the First Order during their war against the Resistance. During her service aboard Commander Pyre and Agent Tierny's Star Destroyer, Galek trained a batch of cadets, which included DT-533, DT-798, and Lin Gaava, among others.

Galek was equipped with the standard First Order TIE Fighter Pilot uniform, albeit with a black military rank pauldron. Both her armor and her pauldron were decorated with red livery to denote her status. Galek was killed by Venisa Doza during the blockade of Dantooine.
Lieutenant Galek first appeared in the Star Wars Resistance episode "Live Fire." She is voiced by Christine Dunford. An earlier version of the episode's script had Galek's name as "Jimes."
